 Chicago, IL — KaZoom Kids Books, Inc,  a multicultural, digital-interactive children’s book publishing company, announced today that it will launch May 1, 2017 its Kickstarter campaign. KaZoom is the first interactive digital publishing company in the United States focusing exclusively on the multicultural market, and most precisely Black and Latino readers.
